
md_text = {'markdown': '[Star Neosync on GitHub](https://github.com/nucleuscloud/neosync)\n\n[![NeosyncLogo](https://assets.nucleuscloud.com/neosync/newbrand/logo_text_light_mode.svg)Neosync](https://www.neosync.dev/)\n\n[Log in](https://app.neosync.dev/)\n\n# Secure Your Data.\n\n# Accelerate Development.\n\n### Neosync is a cloud-native data security platform that continuously monitors, detects and automatically protects sensitive data giving your security teams peace of mind and your developers realistic data to use for local development and testing.\n\n[Get a Demo](https://cal.com/evis-drenova-uorbbv/neosync-demo)\n\n![pre](https://www.neosync.dev/images/newflow.svg)\n\n### Trusted by hundreds of companies\n\n![cust_logo](https://www.neosync.dev/images/logos/c2fo_logo.svg)\n\n![cust_logo](https://www.neosync.dev/images/logos/fellow_logo.svg)\n\n![cust_logo](https://www.neosync.dev/images/logos/fpllc_logo.svg)\n\n![cust_logo](https://www.neosync.dev/images/logos/chub_logo.svg)\n\n![cust_logo](https://www.neosync.dev/images/logos/alascologo.svg)\n\n![cust_logo](https://www.neosync.dev/images/logos/throne_logo.svg)\n\n![cust_logo](https://www.neosync.dev/images/logos/jellsmack_logo.svg)\n\n![cust_logo](https://www.neosync.dev/images/logos/siemens_logo.svg)\n\n![cust_logo](https://www.neosync.dev/images/logos/flex_logo.svg)\n\n![cust_logo](https://www.neosync.dev/images/logos/brain_logo.svg)\n\n![cust_logo](https://www.neosync.dev/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Flogos%2Fchalk_logo.png&w=256&q=75)\n\n![cust_logo](https://www.neosync.dev/images/logos/fhm_logo.svg)\n\n60%\n\n#### Less time to get compliant with HIPAA\n\n40%\n\n#### Accelerated Development Cycles\n\n75%\n\n#### Less time to complete Breach Risk Assessments\n\n50%\n\n#### Less time to implement security controls\n\nPlatform\n\n## Unifying Data Discovery + Classification and Protection Into One Platform\n\nMost platforms tell you where you have sensitive data but don\'t help you remediate it. Neosync integrates AI-powered Data Classification, Discovery and Protection into one platform, closing the loop for security teams.\n\n### Agentless Data Discovery\n\nConnect any database or datawarehouse to Neosync\n\n![st](https://www.neosync.dev/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fconns.png&w=1200&q=75)\n\n### AI-powered Data Classification\n\nAutomatically classify sensitive data using AI\n\n![st](https://www.neosync.dev/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fdet.png&w=1920&q=75)\n\n### Flexible Data Anonymization\n\nAutomatically anonymize your sensitive data using our 50+ pre-built Transformers or build your own in order safely use your sensitive data.\n\n![st](https://www.neosync.dev/images/tmappingnew.svg)\n\n### Reliable Orchestration\n\nSync to multiple destinations. Full control over scheduling, retries, back-offs, timeouts and multiple destinations.\n\n![st](https://www.neosync.dev/images/orch.svg)\n\n### Powerful Subsetting\n\nSubset your database by schema, table, column or a custom SQL query. Neosync automatically handles referential integrity.\n\n![st](https://www.neosync.dev/images/subsetSVG.svg)\n\nTestimonials\n\n## Don\'t take our word for it, listen to our customers\n\nCustomers of all sizes, from high-growth startups to public companies use Neosync to anonymize their sensitive data and sync it across environments.\n\n![cust_logo](https://www.neosync.dev/images/logos/fellow_logo.svg)\n\n"We used to have a manual process that would create mock data but it was always out of date, so we switched to Neosync. Now we anonymize our sensitive health data and sync it from production to staging so our developers can have safe data locally for testing. What used to take 2-4 weeks, now only takes 2 days.\n\n![cust_logo](https://www.neosync.dev/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Faustin.jpeg&w=256&q=75)\n\n### Austin Chustz\n\nSenior Engineer\n\n![cust_logo](https://www.neosync.dev/images/logos/alascologo.svg)\n\n"We chose Neosync because of their focus on the developer workflow. Their APIs and SDKs, along with their Terraform provider made it easy to integrate into our workflow. Neosync is able to give the data security that we need for our production data while giving our developers high-quality data that allows them to build fast."\n\n![cust_logo](https://www.neosync.dev/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fbasti.jpeg&w=256&q=75)\n\n### Sebastian Seitz\n\nDirector, Platform Engineering\n\nUse cases\n\n## Neosync is built for engineering teams\n\nWhether you\'re a Developer, Data Engineer or AI/ML Engineer, Neosync can give you the data you need without the privacy and security risks.\n\n[Get a Demo\\\\\n\\*No credit card required.](https://cal.com/evis-drenova-uorbbv/neosync-demo)\n\n### Developers\n\nDesigned to help developers build, test and ship faster by anonymizing production data so you can safely use it locally.\n\n### Data Engineers\n\n### AI/ML Engineers\n\n![Feature preview](https://www.neosync.dev/images/devarch.svg)\n\nPlatform\n\n## Features to Protect your Data and Power your Workflows\n\nNeoysnc has enterprise-grade features with a world-class developer experience that developers love.\n\nData Anonymization\n\nMask, redact, scramble or obfuscate sensitive data in code.\n\nSynthetic Data Generation\n\nChoose from 45+ pre-built Synthetic Data Transformers.\n\nOrchestration\n\nFull control over scheduling, retries back-offs timeouts and multiple destinations.\n\nSubset\n\nSubset your database using one or multiple SQL queries.\n\nCustom Transformers\n\nCreate your own custom transformers in code.\n\nSchema Initialization\n\nInitialize your destination schema and run pre and post-job hooks.\n\nMulti-Destination Syncing\n\nSync data to multiple databases and object storage.\n\nTools for Developers\n\nNeosync ships with a CLI, SDKs & APIs and a Terraform module.\n\nData\n\n## Supports Structured and Unstructured Data\n\nNeosync supports structured data in relational databases and unstructured data in NoSQL databases.\n\n[![NeosyncLogo](https://www.neosync.dev/images/blogs/struc.svg)\\\\\nStructured Data\\\\\n\\\\\nNeosync natively structured data held in relational databases or warehouses.](https://docs.neosync.dev/connections/postgres) [![NeosyncLogo](https://www.neosync.dev/images/blogs/unstruc.svg)\\\\\nUnstructured Data\\\\\n\\\\\nNeosync supports unstructured data in NoSQL databases or even free form text](https://docs.neosync.dev/connections/mongodb)\n\n## Get started today in minutes\n\nJoin hundreds of companies using Neosync to deliver a better local developer experience with anonymized production data.\n\n[Get a Demo\\\\\nNo credit card required.](https://cal.com/evis-drenova-uorbbv/neosync-demo)\n\n![NeosyncLogo](https://assets.nucleuscloud.com/neosync/newbrand/logo_dark_mode.svg)\n\nCompany\n\n[About](https://www.neosync.dev/about) [Roadmap](https://neosync.productlane.com/roadmap) [Pricing](https://www.neosync.dev/pricing) [Trust Center](https://trust.neosync.dev/)\n\nResources\n\n[Documentation](https://docs.neosync.dev/) [Blog](https://www.neosync.dev/blog) [Product](https://www.neosync.dev/product/platform) [Discord](https://discord.com/invite/MFAMgnp4HF)\n\nSolutions\n\n[Test code against anonymized Production data](https://www.neosync.dev/solutions/test-code-anonymized-prod-data) [High quality data for lower-level environments](https://www.neosync.dev/solutions/lower-level-environments) [Easily reproduce Production bugs locally](https://www.neosync.dev/solutions/reproduce-prod-bugs-locally) [Solve GDPR, DPDP, FERPA, HIPAA and more](https://www.neosync.dev/solutions/security-privacy)\n\nLegal\n\n[Privacy Policy](https://www.neosync.dev/privacy-policy) [Terms of Service](https://www.neosync.dev/terms-of-service) [Self-hosted Terms of Service](https://www.neosync.dev/self-hosted-terms-of-service) [Service Agreement](https://www.neosync.dev/msa)\n\n![soc2](https://www.neosync.dev/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fassets.nucleuscloud.com%2Fneosync%2Fmarketingsite%2Fsoc2.png&w=256&q=75)\n\nNucleus Cloud Corp. 2025', 'metadata': {'ogUrl': 'https://www.neosync.dev', 'og:image': 'https://assets.nucleuscloud.com/neosync/marketingsite/mainOGHero.svg', 'language': 'en', 'og:image:height': '630', 'ogDescription': 'Neosync is an open source data anonymization and synthetic data generation platform for developers', 'twitter:description': 'Neosync is an open source data anonymization and synthetic data generation platform for developers', 'twitter:image:alt': 'mainOG', 'og:image:alt': 'mainOG', 'twitter:image:width': '1200', 'ogLocale': 'en_US', 'og:title': 'Neosync | Open Source Data Anonymization and Synthetic Data', 'og:url': 'https://www.neosync.dev', 'favicon': 'https://www.neosync.dev/favicon.ico', 'ogSiteName': 'Neosync', 'twitter:image': 'https://assets.nucleuscloud.com/neosync/marketingsite/mainOGHero.svg', 'viewport': 'width=device-width, initial-scale=1', 'twitter:card': 'summary_large_image', 'og:type': 'website', 'description': 'Neosync is an open source data anonymization and synthetic data generation platform for developers', 'ogTitle': 'Neosync | Open Source Data Anonymization and Synthetic Data', 'twitter:image:height': '630', 'title': 'Neosync | Open Source Data Anonymization and Synthetic Data', 'og:description': 'Neosync is an open source data anonymization and synthetic data generation platform for developers', 'og:site_name': 'Neosync', 'og:locale': 'en_US', 'ogImage': 'https://assets.nucleuscloud.com/neosync/marketingsite/mainOGHero.svg', 'og:image:width': '1200', 'twitter:title': 'Neosync | Open Source Data Anonymization and Synthetic Data', 'scrapeId': 'f2205ecb-89d9-437d-aa9e-324a63b2dbb7', 'sourceURL': 'https://www.neosync.dev', 'url': 'https://www.neosync.dev/', 'statusCode': 200}}